[0.358182, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H\u001b[1;36m### pgSafe — same tool, two shapes, 10 M-row backup head-to-head\r\n###\r\n### Same pgsafe binary. Same source cluster. Same encrypted POSIX repo.\r\n### Run 1: PG-native shape (libpq → pg_basebackup under the hood, single connection).\r\n### Run 2: pgSafe shape  (worker on PG host, 4 StreamFile RPCs in parallel over one SSH session).\r\n"]
[0.358744, "o", "### Shape is inferred from config: pg.host unset → PG-native; --ssh-target set → pgSafe-mode.\r\n\u001b[0m\r\n"]
